<lyrics>[V1]
 kàn nǎ! shén de gāo yáng, tā zǒng shì zài wǒ qián fāng;
 kàn nǎ! shén de gāo yáng tā zǒng shì zài wǒ qián fāng.
 bù yào kàn yún wù mí máng, bù yào kàn dà fēng jù làng
 yǒu shēng yīn shuō kàn nǎ shén de gāo yáng, tā shì yuán shǒu, dào lù fāng xiàng.</lyrics>
<title>kàn nǎ shén de gāo yáng 迦南552</title>
